Words per minute (WPM) is the number of words processed per minute which we use to measure and denote the speed of speech It represents your understanding and information consumption In short, it represents the speed at which your cognitive functions are working at their peak, ensuring the most optimal comprehension, memorization, and How does the Silence Removal work? Saima’s “Silence Removal” functionality identifies the long pauses and dead air during the video and speeds them up for you This will help you stay more focused with your videos, as your brain will not get bored, and you will be less inclined to take your phone and start What is “Focus Boost”? The “Focus Boost” feature is a unique approach designed by our Focus Boost will help you stay much more focused throughout your When this feature is “ON”, Saima tool will automatically increase the video speed in an unnoticeable manner - you never notice the With this feature, your brain will not get bored with the same voice, tone and speed of the video, and you will be inclined to stay more engaged and Do I need to pay for Saima? Well, we’d prefer you to 😃 BUT, Saima has an package available for everyone and we made sure none of our valuable features are missing from Is Saima available on mobile? We are working tirelessly to deliver our product also on Please hang on with us, this is a very challenging task and our rocket scientists are working on Why should I use Saima when there is a “playback speed option”? You can always use encyclopedias to find information instead of Google or This is the next step in video and audio consumption, aiming to make it efficient and increase our With Saima, you can comprehend and focus much better and save tangibly more speakers and students with ADHD claim that they are much more focused when watching their online lectures with Saima, which is in line with the research conducted by our Chief Neuroscientist Dr Prof How is it possible to slow down the video AND save time? It is possible with 🤩 You can save time even when you play the video at slower than the original With our two SUPERfeatures - Silence Removal and Focus Boost, we remove long pauses and apply an unnoticeable speed increase, which leads to the best experience How do people with attention issues benefit from Saima? Our users with ADD ADHD provided us with feedback that the “Focus Boost” solution helps them to stay focused and avoid being It is assumed that the right speed and its manipulation can essentially contribute to video watching I am a English speaker, how can Saima help me? Yes, this is our 💪 The story behind Saima started with our having a hard time understanding his classes and this is when the idea of personalized video pace was We identify the speed at which your supercomputer “your brain” operates at its best and delivering materials right at the pace ensures better comprehension, memorization, and How can Saima help me understand and memorize my videos better? Every human being has a unique brain Every single person has a different cognitive load To reach the cognitive capacity most optimal usage, everyone should consume online content at their OWN This is exactly when your “SUPER computer” called “the brain” obtains and memorizes the data better and How can you help me with distractions, multitasking, and mind wandering? Have you ever watched something online and caught yourself thinking about anything BUT the actual video you’re watching? Like what you ate yesterday or what to cook tomorrow? Well, science calls this mind You get easily distracted when the speed of the video is not optimal for YOUR personal cognitive When it’s too slow, your mind starts wondering and you lose That is why it is essential for everyone to consume the video not at the pace that’s imposed by content makers, but at their very own Love to hear from you, Get in touch Send Blog Pricing Speed Test How to Company Privacy policy Terms and conditions +1 (408) Shattuck , Berkeley, CA, USA, Saima Technology is USPTO patent pending   Plans & Pricing | Saima How To Blog Company Pricing Speed Test Get for Free Speed Test FAQ Blog Company Pricing Pricing for YOU Choose the right plan for your journey FREE $0 no credit card needed , it’s FREE Unlimited 1 Device Personalized Speed Silence Removal Train The Brain Personal statistics Best option Premium $3.75 Free for limited time Go PREMIUM for FREE Unlimited 3 Device s Unlimited Personalized Speed Unlimited Silence Removal Unlimited Train The Brain Personal Statistics Corporate Let’s Talk Learn more Contact Sales Unlimited ∞ Device s API L&D Dashboard 7 Customer service Dedicated customer success manager Why people love saima Stanford University Graduate Scho

Botanix is a decentralized Layer 2 solution built on the native currency of synthetic It operates using two core components: The Ethereum Virtual Machine : Fortified by a PoS (Proof of Stake) consensus protocol that leverages Bitcoin s PoW (Proof of Work) for superior Stakes are represented by actual bitcoin stored securely within wallets on the Bitcoin The Spiderchain : A dynamic and set of multisigs that secure all the actual bitcoin on The Spiderchain consists of a distributed network of multisigs, safeguarded by a randomized subset of participants, making it a truly decentralized protection What is the Spiderchain? The Spiderchain is a distributed network of multisigs that secure all the actual bitcoin on In the future, it will be a permissionless network, allowing any participant to The name "Spiderchain" stems from envisioning multisigs wallets where each leg of the spider represents a different Every Bitcoin block is associated with a new multisig created between a set of random participants from the Is the Spiderchain secure? Yes, the Spiderchain is meticulously engineered with unparalleled security Even in the unlikely event of an attacker obtaining a 2 3 majority, the Spiderchain s "forward security" design ensures that the underlying bitcoin remains securely locked within older, established This makes it virtually impossible for any potential attacker to steal bitcoin secured by the Is Botanix decentralized? Yes, Botanix is a fully decentralized protocol that stands apart from other Layer 2 The Spiderchain s introduction enables Botanix to be truly decentralized, with no central governing entity or This aligns with Satoshi Nakamoto s vision for a decentralized blockchain Does Botanix need a BIP? No, Botanix leverages Bitcoin s taproot upgrade for its Layer 2 design and does not require any additional BIPs (Bitcoin Improvement Proposals).
